- Extract unique drivers (column A) and unique weekday headers (row 1, columns B‑Y).
- Create/overwrite a sheet named "Summary".
- Write weekday headers in row 1 (starting at B1) and driver names in column A (starting at A2).
- Insert the corrected SUMPRODUCT formula for each driver‑weekday cell.
- Save to the output directory.
